{"tid":1053831,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人鍾意食班戟？","createTime":"2019-03-09T11:17:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T10:13:38.000Z","uid":175988,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0f2bf18600b6f72ff594c94bc9102149a4492b8c","tid":1053831,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:17:43.000Z","msg":"<strong>IHOP New York Cheesecake</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HyNCMr5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHyNCMr5.jpg&h=3b425179&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPancake鬆軟得嚟口感實在，唔似梳乎厘嗰隻成陣風咁。粉漿加咗芝士蛋糕粒幾特別，多咗種creamy嘅酸香，味道層次提升唔少 (不過cheesecake bites分佈唔均勻，咬中先有驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）另外啲whipped cream同candied strawberry都唔錯，可惜糖漿太淡，果味唔濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n整體上配撘合適，唔會太過甜膩，士多啤梨清新嘅酸味同輕盈嘅cream又減輕咗飽滯感，只係糖漿普通啲。$60左右有咁嘅質素同份量都可以接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d1ef0ba99977cabae23ccc7306f4f751ae76e2","tid":1053831,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:46:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d712ffca8fd67df16ccc39c8e2f2000a2afb7cc","tid":1053831,"uid":193020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:16:43.000Z","msg":"邊到有得食？"},{"pid":"40a3ebf146b3527f00a5658b99ffbe0af1305ad5","tid":1053831,"uid":175988,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"1d712ffca8fd67df16ccc39c8e2f2000a2afb7cc","tid":1053831,"uid":193020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:16:43.000Z","msg":"邊到有得食？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:22:07.000Z","msg":"US"},{"pid":"a27794f98e9e250176166c84e24f5688e75f7531","tid":1053831,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:23:17.000Z","msg":"都係嗰句，快啲喺香港開分